commands.name: az devcenter admin project-catalog connect
commands.summary: Connects a project catalog to enable syncing.
commands.syntax:
az devcenter admin project-catalog connect [--catalog-name]
                                           [--ids]
                                           [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                           [--project]
                                           [--resource-group]
                                           [--subscription]

commands.name: az devcenter admin project-catalog create
commands.syntax:
az devcenter admin project-catalog create --catalog-name
                                          --project
                                          --resource-group
                                          [--ado-git]
                                          [--git-hub]
                                          [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                          [--sync-type {Manual, Scheduled}]
                                          [--tags]

commands.name: az devcenter admin project-catalog delete
commands.syntax:
az devcenter admin project-catalog delete [--catalog-name]
                                          [--ids]
                                          [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                          [--project]
                                          [--resource-group]
                                          [--subscription]
                                          [--yes]

commands.name: az devcenter admin project-catalog get-sync-error-detail
commands.summary: Gets project catalog synchronization error details.

commands.name: az devcenter admin project-catalog list
commands.summary: List the catalogs associated with a project.

commands.name: az devcenter admin project-catalog sync
commands.summary: Syncs templates for a template source.
commands.syntax:
az devcenter admin project-catalog sync [--catalog-name]
                                        [--ids]
                                        [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                        [--project]
                                        [--resource-group]
                                        [--subscription]

commands.name: az devcenter admin project-catalog update
commands.syntax:
az devcenter admin project-catalog update [--add]
                                          [--ado-git]
                                          [--catalog-name]
                                          [--force-string {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                          [--git-hub]
                                          [--ids]
                                          [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                          [--project]
                                          [--remove]
                                          [--resource-group]
                                          [--set]
                                          [--subscription]
                                          [--sync-type {Manual, Scheduled}]
                                          [--tags]

commands.name: az devcenter admin project-catalog wait
commands.summary: Place the CLI in a waiting state until a condition is met.
